<F P=106> [POSTFACTUM report: "New Chernobyl Director"] </F>
  [Text] Sergey Parashin has been appointed general director 
of the Chernobyl Atomic Electric Power Station [AES] by the 
decision of Ukraine's Ministry of Atomic Energy collegium. 
Before this he worked as deputy director of the Chernobyl AES 
for economic matters. Taking the position of general director, 
Sergey Parashin stated that he considers it as one of his main 
tasks to convince the public that the Chernobyl AES is no less 
safe than the other nuclear stations of Ukraine. 

